  <uml:Model xmi:id="_p5STsFqCEeeEToh03JBYQA" name="itut-sync">
    <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_cMX14CQKEfC9Ju4nzK2X6A" annotatedElement="_p5STsFqCEeeEToh03JBYQA">
      <body>contact: tsbsg15@itu.int&#xD;
&#xD;
Revisions:&#xD;
&#xD;
2.0.04	2026-04-16		ITU-T G.7721 v2.0.04 (Draft)		Aligned with the latest editions of the PTP Telecom Profiles and SyncPhy ITU-T Recommendations (i.e., ITU-T G.8275.1 v5.0, ITU-T G.8275.2 v4.0, and ITU-T G.781 v6.0).&#xD;
2.0		2025-08-22		ITU-T G.7721 v2.0 (08/2025)		Added the SyncPhy UML information model.&#xD;
1.2		2024-12-07		ITU-T G.7721 v1.2 (12/2024)		Aligned with the latest versions of the PTP telecom profiles in ITU-T G.8265.1 v4.1, ITU-T G.8275.1 v4.2, and ITU-T G.8275.2 v3.2.&#xD;
1.1		2022-11-13		ITU-T G.7721 v1.1 (11/2022)		Aligned the PTP UML information model with the data set defined in IEEE 1588-2019.&#xD;
1.0		2018-11-29		ITU-T G.7721 v1.0 (11/2018)		Initial version.</body>
    </ownedComment>
