          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_7BJ4gRIoEe-aAcddIn44RQ" annotatedElement="_7BJ4gBIoEe-aAcddIn44RQ">
            <body>The path delay measuring mechanism used by the PTP Transparent Clock (TC) Ports in computing &lt;meanDelay> (propagation delay).</body>
          </ownedComment>
