          <body>The Current data set (DS) of the SyncPhy Instance.</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="__R6JEMBEEe6xirORnB-xqg" name="hopsNumber" visibility="public" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_NbhIEMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg" annotatedElement="__R6JEMBEEe6xirORnB-xqg">
            <body>The number of Synchronous Equipment Clock (SEC) nodes from the nearest Synchronization Supply Unit (SSU), Primary Reference Clock (PRC) or enhanced PRC (ePRC) in the synchronization network reference chain.&#xD;
&#xD;
In case the eQL TLV is not received on the port that is selected as current reference of the node, the value of this attribute is implementation specific.&#xD;
&#xD;
Note: the count reported by this attribute is incomplete when the SEC/eSEC chain, started from the originator of the extended QL TLV, is composed of the mixture of SEC and eSEC clocks, as reported by the partialChain attribute.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Integer"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_koOzEAZqEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_BQy3oMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg" name="enhancedHopsNumber" visibility="public" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_ZBd3gMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg" annotatedElement="_BQy3oMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg">
            <body>The number of enhanced Synchronous Equipment Clock (eSEC) nodes from the nearest Synchronization Supply Unit (SSU), Primary Reference Clock (PRC) or enhanced PRC (ePRC) in the synchronization network reference chain.&#xD;
&#xD;
In case the eQL TLV is not received on the port that is selected as current reference of the node, the value of this attribute is implementation specific.&#xD;
&#xD;
Note: the count reported by this attribute is incomplete when the SEC/eSEC chain, started from the originator of the extended QL TLV, is composed of the mixture of SEC and eSEC clocks, as reported by the partialChain attribute.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Integer"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_1Hpy4AZqEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_GHtjQMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg" name="frequencyOffsetFromCkSource" visibility="public" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_lYW7sMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg" annotatedElement="_GHtjQMBFEe6xirORnB-xqg">
            <body>The frequency offset calculated by the frequency offset source performance degradation defect.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Integer"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="__dJAAAZqEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_pwbfkctcEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" name="_sourcePort" isReadOnly="true" association="_pwZDUMtcEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_Gg-50MtdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" annotatedElement="_pwbfkctcEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q">
            <body>The SyncPhy Port selected as reference for the frequency system clock currently.&#xD;
&#xD;
Note: The layerProtocolName of the referenced LayerProtocol instance shall be 'SYNC_PHY'.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:Class" href="../G.7711/itut-core-model.uml#_gROecFYXEeOVGaP4lO41SQ"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_qTTtsMtdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" name="mixedChain" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_qTTtsctdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" annotatedElement="_qTTtsMtdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q">
            <body>Indicates whether the SEC/eSEC chain, started from the originator of the extended Quality Level (eQL) TLV, is composed of only enhanced Synchronous Equipment Clock (eSEC) clocks  or of the mixture of SEC and eSEC clocks.&#xD;
&#xD;
In case the eQL TLV is not received on the port that is selected as current reference of the node, the value of this attribute is implementation specific.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Boolean"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_U0fYEAZrEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_43AAoMtdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" name="partialChain" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_43AAoctdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" annotatedElement="_43AAoMtdEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q">
            <body>Indicates whether the originator of the extended Quality Level (eQL) TLV of the SEC/eSEC chain is the clock at the head of the chain (i.e., a Synchronization Supply Unit (SSU), Primary Reference Clock (PRC) or enhanced PRC (ePRC)) or a clock in the middle of the chain.&#xD;
&#xD;
In case the eQL TLV is not received on the port that is selected as current reference of the node, the value of this attribute is implementation specific.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Boolean"/>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_G_uLMAZsEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
      </packagedElement>
      <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Class" xmi:id="_VjeOYAlxEe6oAqE-At2_yg" name="SyncPhyParentDsPac">
        <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_VvW2oMB-Ee6csOUPxtf2vA" annotatedElement="_VjeOYAlxEe6oAqE-At2_yg">
          <body>The parent data set (DS) of the SyncPhy Instance.</body>
        </ownedComment>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_dQm8AMBGEe6xirORnB-xqg" name="systemClockSourceId" visibility="public" type="_Yj0dwMA7Ee6xirORnB-xqg" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_koXMsMBGEe6xirORnB-xqg" annotatedElement="_dQm8AMBGEe6xirORnB-xqg">
            <body>The clock identity of the originator of the extended Quality Level (eQL) TLV of the system clock.&#xD;
&#xD;
In case the eQL TLV is not received on the port that is selected as current reference of the node, the value of this attribute is implementation specific.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <lowerValue xmi:type="uml:LiteralInteger" xmi:id="_RRYLwAZtEfCYoadliKChew"/>
        </ownedAttribute>
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_fhGX8MBGEe6xirORnB-xqg" name="systemClockSourceQl" visibility="public" type="_m1DF0MtXEe-IysdZWZ9W1Q" isReadOnly="true">
          <ownedComment xmi:type="uml:Comment" xmi:id="_x0RNUMBGEe6xirORnB-xqg" annotatedElement="_fhGX8MBGEe6xirORnB-xqg">
            <body>The quality level (QL) of the originator of the QL TLV and the extended QL (eQL) TLV if supported.</body>
          </ownedComment>
        </ownedAttribute>
      </packagedElement>
      <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Class" xmi:id="_46b78AlxEe6oAqE-At2_yg" name="SyncPhySyncLpPac">
        <ownedAttribute xmi:type="uml:Property" xmi:id="_rz2DsQlyEe6oAqE-At2_yg" name="_portDs" type="_o9WXsAlyEe6oAqE-At2_yg" aggregation="composite" association="_rz1coAlyEe6oAqE-At2_yg"/>
      </packagedElement>
      <packagedElement xmi:type="uml:Class" xmi:id="_o9WXsAlyEe6oAqE-At2_yg" name="SyncPhyPortDs">
