            <body>The timeStatus flag in the received Signalling messages, indicating whether the time of the remote end application is normal or not.</body>
          </ownedComment>
          <type xmi:type="uml:PrimitiveType" href="pathmap://UML_LIBRARIES/UMLPrimitiveTypes.library.uml#Boolean"/>
